--- TESTCASE Update Project - Success - 204 No Content

--- HTTP
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [204]
PUT {{ApiBaseUrl}}{{ProjectsSection}}/{{ProjectId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Website",
  "code": "WEB",
  "managerId": null
}

--- END


--- TESTCASE Update Project - Verify Changes - 200 OK

--- HTTP
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [200]
## TEST-HAS-BODY
GET {{ApiBaseUrl}}{{ProjectsSection}}/{{ProjectId}}

--- TEST
await tp.Test("Project should reflect updated values.", async () =>
{
    dynamic body = await tp.Response.GetBodyAsExpandoAsync();
    Equal("Website", (string)body.name);
    Equal("WEB", (string)body.code);
});

--- END


--- TESTCASE Update Project - Nonexistent Project - 404 Not Found

--- HTTP
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [404]
PUT {{ApiBaseUrl}}{{ProjectsSection}}/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Website",
  "code": "WEB"
}

--- END


